#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/animated_brushes.rst:1
msgid "A brief explanation about animated brushes and how to use them."
msgstr "關於動態筆刷以及如何使用它們的簡要說明。"

#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/animated_brushes.rst:15
msgid "Animated Brushes"
msgstr "動態筆刷"

#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/animated_brushes.rst:17
msgid ""
"Animated brushes are officially called ‘image hoses’, and they're quite fun. "
"They are basically :ref:`brush tips <predefined_brush_tip>` with multiple "
"image files."
msgstr ""
"動態筆刷被正式稱為“圖像軟管”有些軟體也稱“影像水管”，它們非常有趣。 "
"它們基本上是帶有多張圖片的檔案畫筆，提示 :ref:`筆刷技巧 "
"<predefined_brush_tip>` 。"

#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/animated_brushes.rst:19
msgid ""
"The typical way to make them is to first draw the ‘frames’ on a small "
"canvas, per layer:"
msgstr "製作它們的標準方法為首先在小畫布上利用圖層建立“結構”："

#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/animated_brushes.rst:None
msgid "Krita Animated brush tip layer setup."
msgstr "Krita 動態筆刷圖層設定。"

#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/animated_brushes.rst:25
msgid ""
"You can use the :kbd:`Alt +` |mouseleft| shortcut on the layer thumbnails to "
"isolate layers without hiding them."
msgstr "可以用快速鍵 :kbd:`Shift +` |mouseleft| 在不隱藏圖層的情況下隔離檢視圖層。"

#: ../../<rst_epilog>:2
msgid "mouseleft"
msgstr "滑鼠左鍵"

#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/animated_brushes.rst:None
msgid "Animated brush tips isolated layers."
msgstr "動態筆刷技巧隔離圖層。"

#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/animated_brushes.rst:30
msgid "When done you should have a mess like this."
msgstr "完成後，應該會得到這樣混亂的結果。"

#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/animated_brushes.rst:32
msgid ""
"Go into the brush settings (:kbd:`F5` key), and go to predefined brush-tips, "
"and click :guilabel:`stamp`. You will get this window."
msgstr "進入筆刷設定 (:kbd:`F5` key)， 選取筆尖中的 \"預製形狀\"點擊 "
":guilabel:`+印章`。 就會開啟這個介面。"

#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/animated_brushes.rst:None
msgid "Predefined brush tips dialog."
msgstr "新增預製形狀的筆刷視窗。"

#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/animated_brushes.rst:37
msgid "And then use style **animated** and selection mode set to **random**."
msgstr "然後樣式選用**動畫**選擇模式選為**隨機**。"

#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/animated_brushes.rst:39
msgid ""
"Krita uses :ref:`Gimp’s image hose format <file_gih>` which allows for "
"random selection of the images, angle based selection, pressure based "
"selection, and incremental selection."
msgstr "Krita 會使用 :ref:`Gimp的影像軟管格式 <file_gih>` "
"它允許隨機抓取圖像、基於角度、壓力或是其他控制設定。"

#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/animated_brushes.rst:41
msgid ""
"When you create a brushtip, Krita will automatically switch to it for the "
"current brush, but you will always be able to find it in the predefined "
"brushes tab."
msgstr "當建立筆刷時，Krita "
"會自動切換到當前筆尖，但始終可以在預製筆刷選項頁切中找到它。"

#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/animated_brushes.rst:None
msgid "Result of an animated brush."
msgstr "動態筆刷的成果。"

#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/animated_brushes.rst:46
msgid "And now you can use it to paint trees! (for example)"
msgstr "現在可以用它來畫樹了！ （例如）"

#: ../../tutorials/krita-brush-tips/animated_brushes.rst:48
msgid ""
"You can also use animated brush tips to emulate :ref:`bristle brush tips "
"<heightmap_bristle_brush_tips>` that go from very fine bristles to a fully "
"opaque stamp based on pressure, like a dry paintbrush might do. Or make "
"incremental patterns like the ones you see on porcelain."
msgstr ""

